text: Food quality dropped badly recently. Bad service. Don’t order the signature grilled sotong, very salty. When we feedback about the salty food, the waitress said it is normal like that. Won’t never come back again. Expensive, bad quality and poor service!!!!
Food is very delicious especially the curry fish head with lots of vegetables and ingredients, the sambal Lala is very nice too. Highly recommended.

My dad brought me here for a quick breakfast.  Ordered wanton noodles.  Very simple and delicious meal that cost $5, which to me is reasonable.   Noodles texture not too al dente and not too soft.  Char siew was nice and tender.  Wantons are big, juicy and delicious.

Would come back again.

I speak only for the dish I've tried, which is the Roasted Duck Drumstick Noodle.
Roasted Duck is just amazing, meat is tender and the skin is super good. The amount of fat in the duck is perfect.
Noodles are also springy and tasty. I would definitely revisit for other dishes as well.
Great place for yummy foods such as roasted chicken, duck , pork, curry  fish head, Sambal fried rice, Fried garlic pork …… many many more. And they serves foods fast too.
